        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/86ad2f9a487b5e1fc7f14c6d3aebf17a_3654063000826339914.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素战技</color>\n造成3点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> 。生成1张 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量块</color> ，随机置入我方牌库顶部2张牌之中。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "雷锥散射",
        "title": "雷锥散射",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/aebba01f5c8d920339645f679cd512aa_6474646957420346485.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n造成3点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> ， <color=#ffffff>舍弃</color> 手牌中最多3张 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量块</color> ，在对方场上生成 <color=#ffffff>雷锥陷阱</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "不朽亡骸·雷",
        "title": "不朽亡骸·雷",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/2f5fbc2acab943dc5e598980c758f964_7436948679753494232.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>被动技能</color>\n【被动】回合结束时，生成2张 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量块</color> ，随机置入我方牌库顶部10张牌之中。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "噬骸能量块",
        "title": "噬骸能量块",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/c91f35411606350c7340492100653c9a_4921476133014501560.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>事件牌</color>\n随机舍弃1张原本元素骰费用最高的手牌，生成1个我方出战角色类型的元素骰。（每回合最多打出1张）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/531ed6322b0a8f721e6080da7fcd72ce_1531766883888369224.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "雷元素伤害",
        "title": "雷元素伤害",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/a7f398e6632a554920f91b6563f341fa_4878813629788857357.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超载</color> ：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超导</color> ：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>感电</color> ：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害\n【 <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>原激化</color> ：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[ <color=#ffffff>激化领域</color> ]"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "规则术语",
        "title": "规则术语",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/18/59155606/3b5977f18d39185ac0bc802fa291fb5f_6236758675876598852.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>物理伤害</color>\n物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。\n<color=#ffffff>噬骸能量块</color>\n随机 <color=#ffffff>舍弃</color> 1张原本元素骰费用最高的手牌，生成1个我方出战角色类型的元素骰。（每回合最多打出1张）\n<color=#ffffff>舍弃</color>\n通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。\n<color=#ffffff>雷锥陷阱</color>\n所在阵营的角色使用技能后：对所在阵营的出战角色造成2点 <color=#ffacff>雷元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> ：初始为创建时所弃置的 <color=#ffffff>噬骸能量块</color> 张数。（最多叠加到3）\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color>\n此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
